\/07\/blessed-with-kindness\/","url_meta":{"origin":24813,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Rifq: Allah blesses beloved households with kindness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, when Allah loves the people of a household, He allows gentleness to enter with them.\u201d Source: Fawa\u0304'id Ab\u012b Bakr al-Abhar\u012b 18 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24092,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/11\/30\/allah-guide-to-gentleness\/","url_meta":{"origin":24813,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Rifq: Allah guides His beloved to kindness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 30, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Jarir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty rewards for gentleness what He does not give for rudeness. If Allah loves a servant, then He grants him the quality of gentleness. No household is deprived of kindness but that they have been\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32091,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/allah-loves-kindness-easy\/","url_meta":{"origin":24813,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Rifq: Allah loves kindness, making things easy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mughaffal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is gentle and he loves gentleness. He gives for it what is not given for harshness.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani Al-Azimabadi said, \u201cAllah loves gentleness, meaning, kindness\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11646,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/family-allah-rifq-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":24813,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Kindness: Allah lets gentleness enter their home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf\u00a0Allah Almighty intends goodness for a household, He lets gentleness enter their home.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 24427 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625